title: Wagamama
typeOfFood: Japanese, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Asian Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. International franchise chain inspired by Japanese food. Vegetarian items are marked with a V and some can be made vegan like replacing meat with tofu. This location reportedly fries the deep fried tofu first meatstuff every 2 days when frying oil is changed. Has freshly squeezed juices, edamame, goma wakame salad, yasai gyoza (dumplings), and others.
